IfMetricAddressLessIf.description: For the purpose of easing the instancing of addressed and addressless interfaces; this variable takes the value 0 on interfaces with IP addresses and the value of ifIndex for interfaces having no IP address.  On row creation

IfMetricIpAddress.description: The IP address of this OSPF interface.  On row creation

IfMetricTOS.description: The Type of Service metric being referenced. On row creation

IfMetricValue.description: The metric of using this Type of Service on this interface.  The default value of the TOS 0 metric is 10^8 / ifSpeed.
